## Request Flow - Ver Perfil de Usuario

```mermaid
sequenceDiagram
    actor User as Usuario (Browser)
    participant UI as ProfilePage (Server Component)
    participant QH as GetProfileQueryHandler
    participant PR as UserProfileRepository
    participant UR as UserRepository
    participant FR as FollowRepository
    participant DB as Supabase DB

    User->>UI: Navega a /profile/johndoe
    UI->>QH: execute({ username: 'johndoe' })
    QH->>PR: findByUsername('johndoe')
    PR->>DB: SELECT * FROM user_profiles WHERE username = ?
    DB-->>PR: profile data
    PR-->>QH: UserProfile entity
    QH->>UR: findById(profile.userId)
    UR->>DB: SELECT * FROM users WHERE id = ?
    DB-->>UR: user data
    UR-->>QH: User entity
    alt Profile is private && not owner
        QH->>PR: canView(otherUserId)
        QH-->>UI: throw PermissionDenied
    else
        QH->>FR: getFollowers(profile.userId)
        FR->>DB: SELECT * FROM follows WHERE following_id = ?
        DB-->>FR: followers list
        QH->>FR: getFollowing(profile.userId)
        FR->>DB: SELECT * FROM follows WHERE follower_id = ?
        DB-->>FR: following list
        QH-->>UI: GetProfileResult (DTO)
    end
    UI->>User: Render profile page with stats
```

